OL,3,CJudicial review granted over
OL,4,Ccontroversial plans for shopping centre
OL,6,FA judicial review has been granted to
OL,7,Fresidents in the Knowle area of
OL,8,FBristol, who are bidding to stop
OL,9,Fcontroversial plans .
OL,11,FPlanning permission had been approved
OL,12,Fby Bristol City Council to knock down
OL,13,Fthe 50-year-old shopping centre and
OL,14,Freplace it with more than 800 flats.
OL,16,FBut campaigners were opposed to the
OL,17,Fscale of the plans and what they
OL,18,Fdescribe as a 'low level of affordable
OL,19,Fhousing'.
