OL,3,CJudicial review granted over
OL,4,Ccontroversial plans for shopping centre
OL,6,Fbegan after councillors approved the
OL,7,Fdemolition of the shopping centre,
OL,8,Fjust five weeks after the same
OL,9,Fcommittee unanimously refused the
OL,10,Fapplication.
OL,12,FDevelopers are planning to build 820
OL,13,Fhomes as part of a huge mixed-use
OL,14,Fscheme.
OL,16,FSome buildings could reach 12 storeys
OL,17,Ftall, and the development would
OL,18,Finclude a dentist surgery, cinema, and
OL,19,Fcommunity space.
