OL,6,FThe sudden U-turn raised suspicion
OL,7,Famong campaigners, who have now asked
OL,8,Fa judge to inspect how the decision
OL,9,Fwas made.
OL,11,FThe judicial review could eventually
OL,12,Flead to the planning permission being
OL,13,Fquashed.
OL,15,FCampaigner Laura Chapman, who
OL,16,Frequested the judicial review, said it
OL,17,Fwas 'a victory' for all residents.
