OL,6,FShe said: "The High Court have given
OL,7,Fus permission to go ahead with the
OL,8,FBroadwalk Judicial Review. We
OL,9,Fsubmitted five issues that we believed
OL,10,Fneeded to be investigated, and Judge
OL,11,FJarman has agreed that all five of
OL,12,Fthem are legitimately concerning and
OL,13,Fshould be explored by the High Court.
OL,15,F"We have always believed that our case
OL,16,Fis strong, and today's verdict is a
OL,17,Fhugely positive step forward for the
OL,18,Fcampaign."
