OL,6,FLast July after approving the plans,
OL,7,FConservative Councillor Richard Eddy,
OL,8,Fchair of the committee, said: "St
OL,9,FCatherine's Parade was recently dubbed
OL,10,Fby the tabloid media as the saddest
OL,11,Fshopping parade in Britain. My great
OL,12,Ffear was that actually Broadwalk would
OL,13,Fsoon become the same.
OL,15,F"This mixed-use scheme is a clear
OL,16,Fopportunity to give certainty and
OL,17,Fprovide the regeneration of the
OL,18,Fshopping centre with #200 million of
OL,19,Finvestment.
