OL,6,F"Plus we're talking over 500 jobs,
OL,7,Fwhich is no mean feat. If we're not
OL,8,Fsuccessful at appeal, what would be
OL,9,Fthe cost? It could be quite
OL,10,Fconsiderable on the planning budget
OL,11,Fhere in Bristol.
OL,13,F"The almost 10% minimum offered by the
OL,14,Fapplicant is lower than we would
OL,15,Fexpect, but in view of the
OL,16,Fcircumstances and the opportunities
OL,17,Fhere, I think it's worthwhile.
OL,19,F"And we've heard that three housing
OL,20,Fassociations would work with the
OL,21,Fapplicant to augment that further."
